com.vmware.nsx_policy.orgs.projects.vpcs

Class VpcsFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.orgs.projects.vpcs.VpcsFactory

  • public class VpcsFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    VpcsFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.orgs.projects.vpcs package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
